CreateListing.FlexiblePointOne: Free cancellation until 24 hours before check-in (time shown in the confirmation email).
CreateListing.FlexiblePointTwo: After that, cancel before check-in and get a full refund, minus the first night and service fee.
CreateListing.StrictPointOne: Free cancellation for 48 hours, as long as the guest cancels at least 14 days before check-in (time shown in the confirmation email)
CreateListing.StrictPointTwo: After that, guests can cancel up to 7 days before check-in and get a 50% refund of the nightly rate, and the cleaning fee, but not the service fee.
CreateListing.ModeratePointOne: Free cancellation until 5 days before check-in (time shown in the confirmation email).
CreateListing.ModeratePointTwo: After that, cancel before check-in and get a 50% refund, minus the first night and service fee.
